            "text": "<p><strong>We’re Myzo Chocolate</strong>—a family-owned bean-to-bar chocolate company founded by a veteran’s family. We make our chocolate with rare Criollo and Trinitario cacao beans sourced directly from Costa Rican farmers. No middlemen—just honest partnerships. Our chocolate is crafted with love in Ukraine. We strive to create jobs in Ukraine, have a positive socio-economic impact, and share our craft with the world.</p><p>✨ <em>Taste the difference that transparency makes.</em></p>"
