            "caption": "",
            "heading": "The Myzo Story",
            "text": "<p>In 2020, a spontaneous trip to Costa Rica changed everything. We discovered a culture rich in biodiversity, tradition, and joy. Costa Ricans live by the phrase <em>Pura Vida</em>—“pure life.” We took that spirit to heart.</p><p>We’re bringing the vibrant ecosystems of Central America to life—in every bite. From the tropical cacao groves of the Matina River Valley to your kitchen, our chocolate carries the taste of place.</p><p>🍫 <em>Every piece is a passport to somewhere wild and wonderful.</em></p>",
