            "caption": "",
            "heading": "What Makes Our Chocolate Special?",
            "text": "<p>In Costa Rica, cacao is sacred. For generations, the indigenous peoples—the Maya and the Aztecs—cultivated gourmet varieties like Criollo and Trinitario. These beans produce chocolate that’s smooth, fruity, and never bitter.</p>",
