            "text": "<p>We work directly with farmers in the lush Matina valley, nestled between the Talamanca Mountains and the Caribbean Sea. Our ingredients are organic, our process honest, our intentions pure.</p><p>🌸 <em>You’ll taste the jungle, the history, and the heart with every bite.</em></p>",
